<%= content_for :title, "Bean Counting 2024: Your Year on Visualizer" %>
<%= content_for :preheader, "Welcome to a special look back at Your Year on Visualizer." %>
<tr>
  <td class="sm-px-0" style="width: 100%; padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; text-align: left">
    <table style="width: 100%;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table style="width: 100%;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: #fff; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)">
                <h1 style="margin: 0 0 36px; font-size: 36px; line-height: 36px; color: #000">
                  Bean Counting 2024
                </h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  Welcome to a special look back at Your Year on Visualizer.
                  It's a tale about the beans you've fallen in love with, the brews you've perfected, and those cozy, caffeinated moments that have brightened your days.
                  This is <strong>your</strong> coffee story, narrated one delightful sip at a time.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  This isn't just a bunch of numbers; it's a flavorful journey through your year.
                  From the first morning cup to that late-night espresso, let's reminisce over how your coffee game has evolved and celebrate your journey in the world of coffee.
                </p>
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; color: #000">
                  Your Year on Visualizer
                </h2>
                <% if @yearly_brew.shots_this_year.any? %>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                    <%= render partial: "yearly_brew_stat", locals: { title: "Total shots this year", stat: @yearly_brew.shots_this_year.count, diff: @yearly_brew.shots_this_year.count - @yearly_brew.shots_past_year.count } %>
                    <%= render partial: "yearly_brew_stat", locals: { title: "Favorite roaster", stat: @yearly_brew.favorite_roaster, diff: @yearly_brew.favorite_roaster(:past) } %>
                    <%= render partial: "yearly_brew_stat", locals: { title: "Most used profile", stat: @yearly_brew.most_used_profile, diff: @yearly_brew.most_used_profile(:past) } %>
                    <%= render partial: "yearly_brew_stat", locals: { title: "Kg of coffee used", stat: @yearly_brew.amount_beans_used, diff: (@yearly_brew.amount_beans_used.to_f - @yearly_brew.amount_beans_used(:past).to_f).round(2) } %>
                  </p>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                    But this is just a tiny taste! <strong>See all your stats on <%= link_to "Visualizer Yearly Brew", yearly_brew_index_url, class: "hover-no-underline", style: "color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline", target: "_blank" %></strong> and feel free to share it far and wide. ü•≥
                  </p>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                    P.S.: There are still a couple of days left to upload a shot or two and make your stats even more impressive. üòâ
                  </p>
                <% else %>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                    You haven't uploaded any shots this year. üòî
                  </p>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                    But there are still a couple of days left to upload a shot or two so even you will have something to see on <%= link_to "Visualizer Yearly Brew", yearly_brew_index_url, class: "hover-no-underline", style: "color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline", target: "_blank" %>.
                  </p>
                <% end %>
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; color: #000">
                  Visualizer v4
                </h2>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  In case you missed it, Visualizer has undergone an exciting upgrade with Visualizer V4!
                  From a new logo to infinite loading everywhere, Instant Filters, and tons more, V4 aims to make your coffee data tracking and analysis even more enjoyable. üöÄ
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  To dive into all the details and discover what's new, check out the <a class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline" href="https://visualizer.coffee/updates/visualizer-v4" >full update post</a>.
                </p>
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; color: #000">
                  Emails
                </h2>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  This is the first time I'm sending out a newsletter to all Visualizer users.
                  I hope you don't mind me reaching out to you this way, but if you do, you can <a class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline" href="https://visualizer.coffee/profiles/edit">unsubscribe from future emails in your profile</a>. üôè
                </p>
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; color: #000">
                  Happy holidays!
                </h2>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000;">
                  As we wrap up this year, I can't help but feel incredibly grateful for your participation in the Visualizer community.
                  Your shared shots and passion for coffee have been a source of inspiration, making the platform a vibrant and engaging space for coffee enthusiasts.
                  Your contributions have helped shape Visualizer into what it is today, and for that, I am sincerely thankful. ü•∞
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000;">
                  As a small token of my appreciation, and to add a little extra joy to your coffee
                  experiences, I've arranged a special deal with my <strong>favorite roaster</strong>,
                  <a href="https://banibeans.si/" class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline">Banibeans</a>. Use the code
                  <code style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: #e5e5e5; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; color: #262626">VISUALIZER10</code> in
                  <a href="https://banibeans.si/pages/shop" class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline;">the shop</a>
                  to enjoy a 10% discount on your purchase. ‚ú®
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000;">
                  Whether you're decorating the Christmas tree, lighting the menorah, raising an aluminum pole, or celebrating in your own special way, I wish you happiness and cheer. üéÑ
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000;">
                  Here's to a new year filled with health, happiness, and, of course, fantastic coffee.
                  Both me and Visualizer are looking forward to all your shots in the upcoming year! ‚òï
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000;">
                  Miha
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>
